+ * 	- changes refs to dev->ethtool_ops to ethtool_ops
+ * 	- changed dev_ethtool to ethtool_ioctl
+ *      - remove EXPORT_SYMBOL()s
+ *      - added _kc_ prefix in built-in ethtool_op_xxx ops.
+ */
